Interface ConfigurableEntityEditor

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface ConfigurableEntityEditor
extends DescribedEntity
    An entity that can be configured. Top interface for Configuration Editors. Implementations can edit local or remote configuration entities.
